data.description: Welcome to 694 Millhouse Drive!  A spacious townhome in the sought after community of Millhouse Creek, a small personable community with its own prestigious identity.  Featuring 3 bedrooms, two full baths and two powder rooms.  Nestled between lush trees, this charming townhome boasts a picturesque wooded landscape at the front and back, offering serene views of nature from every angle.  One of the larger homes with a three level bumpout, full size rear deck and upper level balcony.  The heart of the home is the kitchen, featuring granite counters, 42 inch cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a stunning island - the perfect hub for gatherings and culinary adventures. The large living room, dining room, and main level family room share the common element of hardwood floors, creating a cohesive and inviting atmosphere.  Upstairs you'll find the primary bedroom with cathedral ceilings, a large walk-in closet, secondary closet, primary bath with dual sink vanity, soaking tub and private balcony. Two additional bedrooms, hall bath with dual sink vanity and laundry.  The lower level features a spacious family room and secure walk-out slider to patio.  Two car garage and driveway make this home perfect.  One year warranty.  A prime location for commuters to Ft. Meade, DC, Baltimore, and Annapolis. You'll LOVE it!  ***VA Assumable loan for qualified VA buyer***
